        <headline>Severe Thunderstorm Warning issued June 6 at 12:52AM CDT until June 6 at 1:30AM CDT by NWS Amarillo TX</headline>
        <description>At 1251 AM CDT, a severe thunderstorm was located over Slapout, or 15
miles west of Laverne, moving east at 35 mph.

HAZARD...60 mph wind gusts and quarter size hail.

SOURCE...Radar indicated.

IMPACT...Minor damage to roofs, siding, and trees is possible. Hail
damage to vehicles is expected.

Locations impacted include...
Slapout.
</description>
        <instruction>For your protection move to an interior room on the lowest floor of a
building.

Torrential rainfall is occurring with this storm, and may lead to
flash flooding. Do not drive your vehicle through flooded roadways.</instruction>
